						Tel Aviv
						<br/>
						Many other countries
					</div>
				</div>
				<div style="padding-top:5px;">
					<div style="color:black;">
						Address:
					</div>
					<div id="full_name" style="color:gray;font-size:14px;padding-left:5px;">
						4th floor, building 8, Kiryat Atidim Towers
						<br/>
